}

### 상품 조회(특정 카테고리 조회)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/products?categoryId=5977009092038656
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{

}

### 상품 조회(가격 범위 지정)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/products?categoryId=5977009092038656
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{

}

### 상품 조회(이름 + 가격 범위 검색)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/products?productName=맨투맨&minPrice=500&maxPrice=150000
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{

}

### 상품 조회(카테고리 + 가격 범위 + 정렬)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/products?categoryId=5&minPrice=10000&maxPrice=20000&sort=price,asc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{

}

### 상품 조회(페이징 적용)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/products?page=0&size=10
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{

}

### 상품 조회(모든 조건 혼합)
GET http://localhost:10000/api/v1/products?productName=맨투맨&categoryId=5977009092038656&minPrice=10000&maxPrice=400000&page=0&size=20&sort=createdAt,desc
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{at}}

{

}
